{"tid":493453,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"求一首日文歌","createTime":"2017-12-08T14:04:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-09T11:20:34.000Z","uid":72900,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"17f77c4398565457e8c9931927251afb192b2276","tid":493453,"uid":72900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T14:04:58.000Z","msg":"因為首歌好好聽，想聽番但冇從入手<br />\n<br />\n得以下資料，求巴絲幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. 首歌係YOUTUBE 廣告來，時間大概係2016年在5-8月咁上下。果時聽李克勤我是歌手合集（一個鐘長果段），係中間啲插播廣告來（廣告得來成段都係歌，冇其他野好似係）<br />\n<br />\n2. 日文，女仔唱嘅。利伸 唔識日文 唔記得啲歌詞<br />\n<br />\n真係好好聽，不過得咁少資料 有冇巴絲有頭緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98e7c1b03bc625d0e1244ae96a525b5953949800","tid":493453,"uid":156331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T14:06:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db9b7f9c9dc4fd4895c1a17fae58ea41474ae001","tid":493453,"uid":72900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T14:08:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哼出黎都易d估呀 <br />\n困陣有人打左首前前前世出黎 都有巴打估到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成年冇聽過 冇概念 <br />\n<br />\n首歌好日本 唔係快歌 係情歌類"},{"pid":"7493fd59c7f1b4e00773aa2d59d1e29c0655fb5f","tid":493453,"uid":86500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T14:08:59.000Z","msg":"旋律都無點幫？"},{"pid":"b4c4e634789c97c591dcb148eefa87dfa86771dc","tid":493453,"uid":136769,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T14:08:59.000Z","msg":"會吾會係賣雪糕個首??"},{"pid":"30fb7e241aa16d27e3c6923b6844885df31e9f3a","tid":493453,"uid":72900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T14:10:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>旋律都無點幫？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n類似 仁醫主題曲果類咁（女仔唱果首） 好似係"},{"pid":"7e6d7955e1fc33ff7deb778d3df40ccaa852b74b","tid":493453,"uid":72900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T14:10:31.000Z","msg":"<blockqu